lines: You find a dust-ridden file cabinet, and open it to uncover its contents
A pile of boxes laying on the floor, maybe there are some valuables inside?
Those packages seem to have the EdgeRunner logo stamped on them. I wonder who they were meant for... well, they're yours now!
After minutes of searching, You finally located a box of loot.
You came upon containers in the midst of a room and open them to see what's inside.
You came across a kitchen and decide to investigate the contents of the cabinets.
You find a stack of crates emblazoned with the Maikon logo. May as well take a peek inside.
You stumbled to an old, abandoned workbench and hastily searched it for valuables.
